title: Editorial Cartoons of the Week (PHOTOS)
text: The ones about Biden were offensive, his Son died, I don't know how I could cope if my only Son died before me, yeah my Granddog is laying against my back right now. First dog walk today, I took him out for a poop, yes I pick it up, the next two longer walks he takes me out for a walk, he stops and sniffs the delicate fragrances left in the park next to our home, it is amazing how a 7 lb dog can lock up his all foot drive and make me stop walking while he sniffs delicate odors. I would post his picture, but unlike rawstory, this site will not let me post a picture of the best dog in the whole wide world.
